title: Fully renovated, brand new appliances, washer and dryer in unit
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to The Rodney!Located in the hillside neighborhood of Los Feliz, The Rodney is just around the corner from what is considered the most pedestrian-friendly street in Los Angeles, Hillhurst Ave.', 'This beautiful pet-friendly community offers renovated spacious 1 and 2 bedroom floorplans with modern upgrades and in unit washer and dryer.', ' Here you will be able to feed your soul with the area’s best eateries or enjoy drinks at world-class cocktail lounges.', 'For the outdoor enthusiasts, you can catch a performance at the Greek Theatre, stargaze at Griffith Observatory or hike one of the state’s largest parks, Griffith Park; All of which are minutes from your doorstep.', 'Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., CA - License # 01834798', '-Air Conditioner', '-Fireplace', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Controlled Access/Gated', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Dishwasher', '-Cable Ready', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Gas Range', '-Microwave', '-Elevator', '-Courtyard', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
